        <num>CC 1396</num>
        <heading>1396.  Prescription of action of warranty</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 1396.  Prescription of action of warranty.
The action of warranty among coheirs is prescribed by five years, and the time commences to run, to wit: for the property included in the partition, from the day of the eviction; and for debts, from the day that the insolvency of the debtor is established by the discussion of his effects.</p>
        </content>
